      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new streetwear line for my brand and i want to make sure it feels authentic to urban culture. i really don't want it to look like cultural appropriation or feel \"fake.\" can you help me define what the core aesthetic and vibe of real urban culture is so i can stay true to it?",
